<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="nav-logo"><span class="taxmate-animated">Tax Mate</span></div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/taxbot">TaxBot</a>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
        <div id="voice-assistant-container" style="position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:9999;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:0.5rem;">
            <button id="voice-assistant-btn" title="AI Voice Assistant" style="padding:0.7rem 1.2rem;border-radius:50%;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;border:none;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.18);cursor:pointer;font-size:1.5rem;">
                <span aria-label="Voice Assistant" style="font-size:2rem;">🎤</span>
            </button>
            <span id="voice-assistant-status" style="background:#fff;color:#2563eb;padding:0.4rem 1rem;border-radius:0.7rem;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.18);font-size:1.1rem;max-width:220px;text-align:right;"></span>
        </div>

    <div class="form-container">
        <h1>Learn Center</h1>
        <p>Educational resources about income tax filing in India</p>
        
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card card-automate">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">📋</div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Basic Concepts</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p class="card-description">Master the fundamentals of income tax</p>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <ul class="card-features">
                            <li>What is Income Tax?</li>
                            <li>Understanding PAN & TAN</li>
                            <li>Financial Year vs Assessment Year</li>
                            <li>TDS explained simply</li>
                            <li>Tax slabs and rates</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="card-benefits">
                            🎯 Perfect for beginners starting their tax journey
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card card-suggestions">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">💰</div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Deductions Guide</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p class="card-description">Maximize your savings with proper deductions</p>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <ul class="card-features">
                            <li>Section 80C (₹1.5 Lakh)</li>
                            <li>Section 80D (Health Insurance)</li>
                            <li>HRA Exemption rules</li>
                            <li>Home Loan Interest benefits</li>
                            <li>Other chapter VI-A deductions</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="card-benefits">
                            💡 Learn to save maximum legally!
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card card-compare">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Tax Regimes</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p class="card-description">Old vs New regime complete analysis</p>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <ul class="card-features">
                            <li>Old vs New regime comparison</li>
                            <li>Which regime to choose?</li>
                            <li>Switching between regimes</li>
                            <li>Salary structure optimization</li>
                            <li>Case studies and examples</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="card-benefits">
                            ⚖️ Make informed decisions about tax regimes
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card card-extract">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">📑</div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Documents</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p class="card-description">Understand all tax-related documents</p>
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <ul class="card-features">
                            <li>Form-16 Explained in detail</li>
                            <li>Form-26AS (Tax Credit)</li>
                            <li>Salary Slips decoding</li>
                            <li>Investment Proofs required</li>
                            <li>ITR forms explained</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="card-benefits">
                            📁 Never miss important documents again!
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>